  audioProfileName: 
  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'It seems your universe was destroyed but your body was not in it.


      That
      explains why you technically didn''t die.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: How Is That Possible?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: I've never seen it happen before
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Like Never?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Never...


      But this means you can travel back to any point
      in time to try to stop the destruction.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Finally, some good news
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Without a past self to meet, you can''t create any paradoxes.


      Of
      course, you''ll need a body to travel anywhere outside the Soul Forge...'
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: But I don't have a body...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Return to the Guardian of Souls.


      Maybe it knows how you
      can get get a body.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Thank You
  prerequisiteConditions: []
